  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2025-01-15",
    "date": "2025-04-15T12:52:10Z",
    "text": "Nuclear Waste Informed Consent Act\n\nThis bill prohibits the Department of Energy (DOE) from using the Nuclear Waste Fund for certain activities related to radioactive waste disposal unless DOE has entered into a written agreement for a repository with (1) the governor of the\u00a0state in which the proposed repository will be located, (2) affected local governments, (3) local\u00a0governments contiguous to the affected local governments if spent nuclear fuel or high-level radioactive waste will be transported through them for disposal at the repository, and (4) affected Indian tribes."
